author: P.R. Venkat
title: TPG-Backed Northstar to Close $800 Million Funding Round
text:
SINGAPORE—Northstar Group, which counts U.S. private-equity giant TPG Capital as a shareholder, will soon close an $800 million funding round, the latest company to join the list of firms seeking to hold cash for investment opportunities in a volatile Asia market.
